  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch tohs eeraudſijis/ tezzeja teem pretti / no ta Dſih- wokta Durwis / un klannijahs lihds patt Seimmei / un fazzija:\nKUNGS/ ja es jelle Schehlaſti- bu efmu atraddis tawas Azzis/ tad ne eij/luhdsains/tawam Kal- pam fezzen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Juins taps atneſts kahds Masums Lihdens/ un magajeet fawas Rahjas/ un peefleedsajtees appaffch ſcha Kohka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es Dabbufchu kahdu Maises Kummofu/ ka juhs fawu Sirdi atſpirđſinajat / pehz war- rat juhs eet/ jo tapehz effat juhs pee juhsfu Kalpu nahkuſchi/ un tee fazzija: Darri/ ka tu eſti fazzijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms tranzahs us to Dſihwokli pee Saras/ un fazz- ija: Steidſecs/ nemm tihjato Miltu trihs Niehrus / mihz un darri Karraſchas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms notezzeja pee Lohpeim/ un nehme weenu mihe- ſtu un labbu Tekfu / un deive to tam Puſcham/ un tas tranzahs to fataifſht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nehme Sweestu nn Peem/ un to Tekfu/ ko wiꞥſch bij fataifsijts / un zehle teem preck- ſcha/ un ſtahweja pats pee teem appaffch Kohka/ un tee ehde.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tee us winnu: Kur irr Sara tawa Seewa? un wiꞥſch fazzija: Redsi/ teju Dſih- wokſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija: Es patee- fi ateefchu pee terwi (zittā Gad-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Ahbraäms un Sara bija wezzi / un dauds Deena- peedſihwojuſchi/ un tas bij mitte- jees ar Saru buht/ ka Seewahu mehds buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad finehjahs Sara pat- ti pee ſewis / fazzidama: Buh tad man Kahribā dſihwoht/ pehz ka es nu wezza efmu / un mane Kungs wezzigs irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija us Ahbraänu: Kami irr Sara finehjuſees pahr to / fazzidama warretu es teefchain dſeindeh wezza buhdaina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Buhtu tad jeb kahda Pee ta tam KUNGAM ne eespehja ma? es ateefchu pee tewi ap feh noliktu Laiku / tad buhs Sara weens Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sara leedsahs / fazzidaina/ es ne efmu finehjuſees Jo ta bihjajahs. Un tas fazzija Ne/ tu eſti finehjuſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zeblahs tee Wihr no turrenes/ un greeſahs uhs So domu: Un Ahbraäms gabje a teem/ tohs pawaddidams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija Arrig es preckſch Ahbraäma ap ſtehpſchn/ ko es darri?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Ahbraäms buhs pa weenu leelu un warrenu Tantu un eekſch winna taps wiſti Lau dis wirs Semmes fivehtiti.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
